						               													<description>OMEGA is a strategic game, revisiting in an original way the theme of secret societies.&amp;#10;You play as an apprentice who is trying to join a mysterious organization known as OOTO. For this, you will have to summon the Ancient Spirits to discover the Arcana of the Omega. So, when the ritual ends, the Disciples will decide which apprentice is worthy to join them...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In a Game of OMEGA, you engage in an occult ritual at the end of which will&amp;#10;be designated the new Initiate of the brotherhood. You will summon Spirits with Runes. These Spirits will guide your progress on the Ritual disc in order to access the Arcana.&amp;#10;The first candidate to reach the number 7 Arcana will end the Ritual. Spirits, Runes and Arcana have special powers. You will have to learn to handle them and combine them to hope to be chosen.&amp;#10;There will be many strategies that can lead you to victory, but when you appear before the judges, be sure to have by your side powerful Arcana and, if possible, enough runes to best satisfy each of your Spirits...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
